Beyond the genome: challenges and potential for epigenetics-driven therapeutic 
approaches in pulmonary arterial hypertension.

Hsu JY(1), Major JL(2), Riching AS(1)(2), Sen R(3), Pires da Silva J(2), Bagchi 
